OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FBy ITV News Reporter Rosie Dowsing and
OL,7,FProducer Georgia Ziebart
OL,9,FPeople with a rare eye condition that
OL,10,Fcauses 'frightening' vision loss have
OL,11,Ftold ITV News they believe it was
OL,12,Fcaused by weight-loss medication,
OL,13,Fprompting experts to advise people to
OL,14,Fget their eyes checked before taking
OL,15,Fthe drugs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FIt comes as the UK medicines health
OL,7,Fregulator last month issued a safety
OL,8,Fwarning after receiving three reports
OL,9,Flinking Semaglutide - known by brand
OL,10,Fnames Ozempic, Wegovy and Rybelsus -
OL,11,Fto the incurable eye condition called
OL,12,FNAION (Non-Arteritic Anterior Ischemic
OL,13,FOptic Neuropathy).
OL,15,FNAION is often referred to as an 'eye
OL,16,Fstroke' - it causes sudden, painless
OL,17,Fvision loss - usually in one eye, but
OL,18,Fsometimes in both eyes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FThe condition is thought to be caused
OL,7,Fby reduced blood flow to the optic
OL,8,Fnerve, and risk factors include sleep
OL,9,Fapnoea, high blood pressure and type
OL,10,Ftwo diabetes.
OL,12,FNew research, released on Wednesday
OL,13,Fand published in the British Journal
OL,14,Ffor Opthalmology, shows that the
OL,15,Fweight-loss jab Wegovy may carry the
OL,16,Fhighest risk of sudden sight loss
OL,17,Fcompared to other Semaglutide drugs.
OL,19,FWegovy is approved on the NHS to help
OL,20,Fpeople lose weight in higher doses.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FOzempic uses lower doses to treat type
OL,7,F2 diabetes, along with Rybelsus, which
OL,8,Fis a pill rather than a jab.
OL,10,FPeter Osler, 68, from Harrogate, has
OL,11,FNAION in both eyes and believes he got
OL,12,Fit because he was prescribed Ozempic
OL,13,Ffor diabetes.
OL,15,FHe lost his peripheral vision and
OL,16,Fdescribes his sight as like looking
OL,17,Fthrough binoculars. After being
OL,18,Fdiagnosed with NAION, he had to give
OL,19,Fup work and driving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FPeter said: "The common thread going
OL,7,Fthrough NAION is you wake up with it.
OL,8,FBut I wasn't asleep when it happened.
OL,9,FI didn't have high blood pressure,
OL,10,FI've never had high blood pressure.
OL,12,F"In my mind, (Ozempic) is the only
OL,13,Fthing that caused it."
OL,15,FPeter added that although he has
OL,16,Fdiabetes, it has always been well-
OL,17,Fmanaged. He said he never had any
OL,18,Findication of diabetic eye problems
OL,19,Fsuch as diabetic retinopathy, for
OL,20,Fwhich he continues to be tested for on
OL,21,Fa yearly basis.
OL,26,@nD@MOUtD@AOUtD@NpmtD@VpnuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FPeter says he feels "validated" by the
OL,7,FMHRA warning and a number of studies
OL,8,Fthat suggest that, although it is
OL,9,Fstill rare, there is an increased risk
OL,10,Fof developing NAION when taking
OL,11,FSemaglutide.
OL,13,FHe says he is concerned about the
OL,14,Fwidespread use of Semaglutide for
OL,15,Fweight-loss, given he was only on a
OL,16,Flow dose as diabetes medication.
OL,18,F"I was on 1 milligram a week, that's
OL,19,Finjected into your stomach. People
OL,20,Ftaking it for weight-loss can take up
OL,21,Fto 12 pens a week.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F"In my view I was only taking a very
OL,7,Fsmall dosage of Ozempic, and I've gone
OL,8,Fblind through it. What are the risks
OL,9,Fof someone taking ten times that
OL,10,Famount?
OL,12,F"My experience is very frightening.
OL,13,FVery life changing. It's the loss of
OL,14,Fmobility, the loss of freedom, and
OL,15,Fhaving to depend on others."
OL,17,FFurther research has suggested the
OL,18,Fodds of NAION were almost five times
OL,19,Fhigher with Wegovy than Ozempic, and
OL,20,Fmore than three times higher in men
OL,21,Fthan in women.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FOne man from Hertfordshire told ITV
OL,7,FNews he had been taking Ozempic and
OL,8,Fthen Wegovy before he developed NAION
OL,9,Fin one eye.
OL,11,FHe wished to remain anonymous because
OL,12,Fhe feels there is a stigma surrounding
OL,13,Fthe irreparable damage caused to his
OL,14,Fsight, and he doesn't want it to
OL,15,Fimpact his work.
OL,17,FThe man, whom ITV News is calling
OL,18,FMiles, had no pre-existing health
OL,19,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F"Now that I understand the
OL,7,Fimplications for me, I regret taking
OL,8,Fthe weight loss medication," he told
OL,9,FITV News.
OL,11,F"I think it's a very positive drug
OL,12,Fthat impacts many many people. I do
OL,13,Fthink that because of the risk, people
OL,14,Fshould be made aware."
OL,16,FMiles said he has been left "in fear"
OL,17,Fof a second NAION event, which could
OL,18,Flead to him losing more of his sight.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@\O]sD@AOUvD@VO]xD@]OUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F"The impact on people's lives is
OL,7,Fimmense," he said. "Potentially, you
OL,8,Fcould be completely blind. It's
OL,9,Fextremely frightening."
OL,11,FMiles has been told by doctors that he
OL,12,Fhas a crowded optic nerve, known as a
OL,13,F'disk at risk'.
OL,15,FIf he had an eye health check before
OL,16,Ftaking the weight-loss medication,
OL,17,Fthis crowded optic nerve would have
OL,18,Fbeen a red flag or a warning not to
OL,19,Fcontinue treatment.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@IO]oD@TOUqD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F'This is a catastrophic, life-changing
OL,7,Finjury'
OL,9,FTodd Engel is one of at least 20
OL,10,Fpeople in the United States taking
OL,11,Flegal action against Novo Nordisk, the
OL,12,Fcompany who produce Ozempic and
OL,13,FWegovy, after he suffered NAION in
OL,14,Fboth eyes.
OL,16,FTodd, who lives in Maryland, says he
OL,17,Fwishes he had never started taking
OL,18,FOzempic to treat diabetes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FAfter two 'eye strokes' or NAION
OL,7,Fepisodes, Todd completely lost all his
OL,8,Fvision, and therefore his independence.
OL,10,FHe says his eyes were also his
OL,11,Flivelihood, as a heavy good vehicle
OL,12,Fdriver.
OL,14,FTodd told ITV News: "This is not just
OL,15,Fa side effect. This is a catastrophic
OL,16,Flife-changing injury.
OL,18,F"I will never ever be able to see my
OL,19,Fwife's beautiful face, any of my
OL,20,Fchildren or grandchildren. I won't be
OL,21,Fable to play ball with my grandkids."
OL,26,@vD@UOUzD@AOU}D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FTodd's wife Shelley says their life
OL,7,Fchanged overnight, and all future
OL,8,Fplans of travelling as part of their
OL,9,Fretirement went out the window.
OL,11,FThe UK and European medicines
OL,12,Fauthorities have added NAION as an
OL,13,Fadverse effect on the product
OL,14,Finformation for Ozempic and Wegovy,
OL,15,Fbut the US medicines agency (FDA) has
OL,16,Fnot.
OL,18,FShelley said: "We are hoping that
OL,19,FNAION will become part of the warning
OL,20,Flabel, to give people the choice to
OL,21,Fmake this decision on their own.
OL,26,@zD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F"Had Todd known this would be the
OL,7,Feffect of medication that was supposed
OL,8,Fto help him, he wouldn't have taken
OL,9,Fit."
OL,11,F'This could be prevented with an eye
OL,12,Fcheck up'
OL,14,FSome retrospective studies show a link
OL,15,Fbetween Semaglutide-use and NAION, but
OL,16,Fhealth professionals say more research
OL,17,Fis needed to establish a causal link
OL,18,Fbetween them.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FAfter reviewing all available data,
OL,7,Fthe European Medical Agency's (EMA)
OL,8,Fsafety committee concluded that NAION
OL,9,Fis a very rare side effect of
OL,10,FSemaglutide - meaning it may affect up
OL,11,Fto 1 in 10,000 people taking the drug.
OL,13,FIt added that adults with type 2
OL,14,Fdiabetes have a two-fold increase in
OL,15,Fthe risk of developing NAION compared
OL,16,Fwith people not taking the medicine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FThe UK medicines regulator (the MHRA)
OL,7,Fsaid: "Non-arteritic anterior ischemic
OL,8,Foptic neuropathy (NAION), a condition
OL,9,Fthat can cause sudden deterioration in
OL,10,Fvision, usually in one eye at a time,
OL,11,Fhas been very rarely reported in
OL,12,Fassociation with Semaglutide in the
OL,13,Ftreatment of type 2 diabetes, weight
OL,14,Fmanagement and cardiovascular risk
OL,15,Freduction.
OL,17,F"Patients reporting a sudden loss of
OL,18,Fvision (including partial loss) while
OL,19,Fon Semaglutide treatment should be
OL,20,Furgently referred for ophthalmological
OL,21,Fexamination."
OL,26,@oD@GOUyD@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FDr Sui Wong, a neuro-ophthalmologist
OL,7,Fat Moorfields Eye Hospital, says
OL,8,Fpatients have come to her with
OL,9,Fconcerns about the link between weight-
OL,10,Floss medication and vision loss.
OL,12,FShe said that even though the risk is
OL,13,Fsmall, "for the person who experiences
OL,14,Fit, they'd be saying they wish they'd
OL,15,Fknown in the first place. So, having
OL,16,Fthis kind of informed conversation is
OL,17,Fimportant.
OL,26,@uD@HOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F"The key thing is people should have
OL,7,Fan informed discussion to decide on
OL,8,Fthe risks they would be taking, and as
OL,9,Fpart of that they can go and get an
OL,10,Feye check to be part of that informed
OL,11,Fdecision."
OL,13,FNovo Nordisk, which produces Ozempic
OL,14,Fand Wegovy, is based in Denmark, where
OL,15,F12 people have won compensation after
OL,16,Fclaiming the drug caused them
OL,17,Fincurable vision loss, or NAION.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,FIn response to this ITV News
OL,7,Finvestigation, Novo Nordisk said:
OL,8,F"Patient safety is our top priority,
OL,9,Fand we take any reports about adverse
OL,10,Fevents from the use of our medicines
OL,11,Fvery seriously. We work closely with
OL,12,Fauthorities and regulatory bodies from
OL,13,Faround the world to continuously
OL,14,Fmonitor the safety profile of our
OL,15,Fproducts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31720
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1773263166
OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F"The EU SmPC and patient leaflets for
OL,7,FWegovy, Ozempic, (Semaglutide
OL,8,Finjection) and Rybelsus have been
OL,9,Fupdated to include "Non-arteritic
OL,10,Fanterior ischemic optic neuropathy
OL,11,F(NAION)" and under section 4.4
OL,12,F"Special warnings and precautions for
OL,13,Fuse" and as an adverse drug reaction
OL,14,Fin section 4.8 "Undesirable effects"
OL,15,F(frequency: very rare, meaning it may
OL,16,Feffect up to 1 in 10,000 people taking
OL,17,FSemaglutide).
