OL,3,CPatients tell ITV News of rare sudden
OL,4,Cblindness linked to weight-loss jabs
OL,6,F"Based on the totality of evidence we
OL,7,Fconcluded that the data did not
OL,8,Fsuggest a reasonable possibility of a
OL,9,Fcausal relationship between
OL,10,FSemaglutide and NAION and Novo Nordisk
OL,11,Fbelieves that the benefit-risk profile
OL,12,Fof Semaglutide remains favourable.
OL,14,F"We recommend that any patients
OL,15,Fexperiencing side effects while taking
OL,16,Four medicines report them to their
OL,17,Fhealthcare provider and in the UK, use
OL,18,Fthe MHRA Yellow Card scheme."
